{"tid":1633762,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"救救自己友！深水埗單野有藍絲屌柒個消防員 想搞到人冇左份工！","createTime":"2019-10-07T05:08:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T12:03:02.000Z","uid":112933,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"7fab8c8e989217d043cdd50039881c835a622027","tid":1633762,"uid":112933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:08:15.000Z","msg":"深水埗仆街司機撞人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有藍絲屌柒個消防員 話佢唔救人<br />\n依家佢畀上頭照肺<br />\n需要表揚信 表揚消防員<br />\n<br />\n以下template 一人一信！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就有關2019年10月6日星期日<br />\n深水埗的士司機撞向行人路事件<br />\n感謝消防隊伍在短時間內到達現場了解情況，急救被車禍撞到受傷市民。 雖當時情況混亂危急，消防人員仍然表現專業，迅速處理現場所有傷者。<br />\n香港人，支持消防員<br />\n<br />\n日期<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWe highly appreciated your fireman's professional medical care on 6 Oct 2019 at a traffic accident in  Sham Shui Po  Although the  condition is very chaotic, your staff acted professionally and treated the patients timely and orderly. <br />\n<br />\nBest regards<br />\nxxxxxx<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日期 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n消防安全總區總部-<br />\n<br />\nEmail : fschq@hkfsd.gov.hk<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n消防安全總區總部<br />\n電話 : 2170 9624<br />\n傳真 : 2312 0376<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一般查詢/投訴-<br />\n電郵 : hkfsdenq@hkfsd.gov.hk<br />\n熱線 : 2723 8787<br />\n傳真 : 2311 0066<br />\n<br />\n幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c7d62ddc91afc37b00dce5ae9d5e3f23c29f6a8","tid":1633762,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:08:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72d3e0a784315ef08d77767ecccff30525d3ea68","tid":1633762,"uid":112933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:09:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef179f0cf57f1c7f96c3e18c11e7f29558f710be","tid":1633762,"uid":22121,"like":0,"dislik